                <h2>1. 为什么你的 Google 账户总被封？</h2>
<p>近期，Google Ads 的风控政策进一步收紧，大量出海企业遭遇了“规避系统（Circumventing Systems）”的封号提示。<br />
这往往不是因为恶意违规，而是因为<strong>不合规的账户操作习惯</strong>：<br />
- 多个账户共用同一张虚拟信用卡或同一个 IP 环境。<br />
- 落地页存在跳转代码、隐藏文本或是未完善的隐私政策（Privacy Policy）。<br />
- 短期内频繁大幅度修改广告预算和出价。</p>
<h2>2. 核心防封要素与资产隔离</h2>
<p>要想在 Google Ads 生态中长期稳定投放，<strong>资产隔离</strong>是重中之重。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>"鸡蛋不要放在一个篮子里，但更重要的是，不要让系统认为这些篮子属于同一个人。"</p>
</blockquote>
<h3>解决方案：</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>环境隔离</strong>：使用纯净的指纹浏览器和独立的住宅 IP 登录不同账户。</li>
<li><strong>资金合规</strong>：使用企业级的海外资金管理系统（如以渔数媒提供的专属开户及虚拟卡服务），确保账单地址与付款人信息的一致性。</li>
<li><strong>网站审查</strong>：确保你的独立站具有清晰的退换货条款、联系方式及无欺诈性声明。</li>
</ol>
<h2>3. 申诉流程全解析</h2>
<p>一旦不幸被封，不要盲目重复提交申诉。<br />
正确的做法是：<strong>先排查，后整理证据，最后写一封逻辑清晰的英文申诉信。</strong><br />
附上你的营业执照、业务模式说明、以及你为了修正错误所做的具体改动截图。真诚且专业的态度，是解封的唯一途径。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="prose max-w-none" x-show="lang === 'en'" x-cloak>
                <h2>1. Why Do Your Google Accounts Keep Getting Banned?</h2>
<p>Recently, Google Ads has tightened its risk control policies, leaving many cross-border enterprises with "Circumventing Systems" account suspensions.<br />
This is often not due to malicious intent, but rather <strong>non-compliant account management habits</strong>:<br />
- Sharing a single virtual credit card or IP environment across multiple accounts.<br />
- Landing pages containing redirect scripts, hidden text, or incomplete Privacy Policies.<br />
- Frequent, massive changes to ad budgets and bids within a short period.</p>
<h2>2. Core Anti-Ban Elements and Asset Isolation</h2>
<p>For long-term, stable advertising within the Google Ads ecosystem, <strong>asset isolation</strong> is paramount.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>"Don't put all your eggs in one basket, but more importantly, don't let the system think all the baskets belong to the same person."</p>
</blockquote>
<h3>Solutions:</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>Environment Isolation</strong>: Use clean anti-detect browsers and dedicated residential IPs for different accounts.</li>
<li><strong>Financial Compliance</strong>: Utilize enterprise-level global fund management systems (like Yiyu Digital Media's exclusive account opening and virtual card services) to ensure billing and payer information match.</li>
<li><strong>Website Audits</strong>: Ensure your site has clear return/refund policies, contact info, and zero deceptive claims.</li>
</ol>
<h2>3. Comprehensive Appeal Process</h2>
<p>If suspended, do not blindly submit repetitive appeals.<br />
The correct approach: <strong>Investigate first, gather evidence, and write a logically sound English appeal letter.</strong><br />
Include your business license, a description of your business model, and screenshots of the specific changes you made to rectify the issue. A sincere, professional attitude is the only path to recovery.</p>
